rows.label: tlk41200122_01_msg0002
rows.name:
They're cute an' fuzzy an' wuzzy
an' they're a really purty n'animal!

rows.label: tlk41200122_01_msg0003
rows.name:
They're s'posed to behave different
in other places, but Gulan Armoo're
really friendly an' gentle! Eeeee!

rows.label: tlk41200122_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Armoo're useful for travel an' stuff too
'cos they can carry stuff...an' yeah,
they're just really, really great!

rows.label: tlk41200122_01_msg0005
rows.name:
An' that's everything I know
about Armoo. An' now you
know everything too!
